title: Intel 12th-gen Alder Lake H-series vs AMD Ryzen 6000 H-series mobile CPUs
content:
Both Intel and AMD made a huge splash at CES 2022 by announcing their new mobile chips that will be powering the next generation of laptops. While Intel unveiled its new Alder Lake mobile chips along with the rest of the 12th-gen desktop parts, AMD decided to announce its new Ryzen 6000 series ‘Rembrandt’ APUs

The post Intel 12th-gen Alder Lake H-series vs AMD Ryzen 6000 H-series mobile CPUs appeared first on xda-developers.
description: In this Intel 12th-gen vs AMD ryzen 6000 comparison, we'll see how the new Alder Lake mobile parts compare against Ryzen 6000 series mobile chips.
